fields.name: Site CSS
fields.value: html, body {     background-color: #333; }  svg {     margin-bottom: 20px; }  .site-logo {     text-align: center;     display: block;     padding: 20px;     border-radius: 20px;     background: white;     box-shadow: 0 0 25px black;     width: 15%;     min-width: 150px;     margin: 32px auto; }  li {     list-style: none;     text-align: center;     margin: 30px 0;     flex-grow: 1;  cursor:pointer;    min-width: 25%; }  h2 {     width: 100%;     text-align: center;     display: inline-block; color: #b5b5b5; }  ul {     display: flex;     flex-direction: row;     margin: 10px auto;     flex-wrap: wrap;     width: 80%;     padding: 0;     justify-content: center; }  hr {     opacity: 0.2;     margin: 10px 0; }  a {     text-decoration: none;     color: white;     font-size: 15px; }  .grow {     transition: all .2s ease-in-out; }  .grow:hover {     transform: scale(1.1); }
